Olivia Bonamy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olivia_Bonamy 0 Olivia Bonamy (born 21 September 1972) is a French actress. She is best known for her appearances in the films Jefferson in Paris, Jacques Audiard's Read My Lips, the thriller Ils and Le ciel, les oiseaux et ta mère.
